@subject: [review of <%= @e['type']%>-request <%= @e['id']%>] requested
<% if @e['sourceproject']-%>
   <%= @e['sourceproject']%>/<%= @e['sourcepackage']%> -> <%= @e['targetproject']%>/<%= @e['targetpackage']%>
<%-end-%>

   https://build.opensuse.org/request/show/<%= @e['id']%>
<% if @e['description']-%>
   Description: <%= @e['description']%><%-end-%>

To REVIEW the request in question against the previous version:
   osc request show --diff <%= @e['id']%>

To ACCEPT the review:
   osc review accept <%= @e['id']%>
   
To DECLINE the review:
   osc review decline <%= @e['id']%> --message="declined for reason xyz (see ... for background / policy / ...)."
